				Why not keep it simple? Let each player pick an alignment (good, evil) with some restrictions such as Ogre, Trolls and Necromancers are always evil. Then good could only PK evil, and evil ... well, being evil, can PK anyone. It'd make for interesting RP. More like a real RP world.		

